# Confusion matrix is a metrics to Evaluate Classification Problem  

# Confusion Matrix 
	Predicted 
Act	TP   FN
	FP	 TN

FP - Type 1 Error
FN - Type 2 Error 


Example : Whether a Person has Disease or Not 

So in this case we should reduce FN: Becase It Predicted Wrong If a patient has disease it predicted You dont have any Disease So in this case You should Try to Reduce Your False Negative.


Precision : To see FP
Recall : To see FN
F : For both 

